Description: MetaStat provides a graphical user interface for conducting
    meta-analyses of continuous and discrete outcomes. It supports
    fixed-effect and random-effects models, subgroup analysis,
    meta-regression, and standard diagnostic visualizations (forest plot,
    funnel plot, Baujat plot). Built with Shiny, it requires no
    programming experience.
